          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chips are cooking, chop your <strong>black olives </strong>finely</p><p>Dice your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> finely</p><p>Chop your <strong>basil</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
