      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Combine your<strong> tomato paste</strong> with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span><strong> cold water</strong>, a pinch of<strong> salt</strong>, <strong>pepper</strong> and <strong>sugar </strong>and the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> (not a fan of raw garlic? Go easy!) in a separate bowl – this is your<strong> garlicky tomato sauce</strong></p>",
