    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chips have been cooking for 15 min, add your <strong>meat-free patty[ies] </strong>to a separate tray (use<strong> tin foil </strong>to avoid mess)</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 10-12 min or until cooked through</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 3 or more? Use 2 trays!</p><p>Slice your<strong> brioche bun[s]</strong> in half, then reassemble</p>",
