    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the patty[ies] has been cooking for 10-12 min, remove the tray[s] from the oven and spoon the<strong> garlicky tomato sauce</strong> over the top</p><p>Top the patty[ies] with a <strong>cheese flavour slice</strong> and add the<strong> sliced brioche bun[s]</strong> to the other side of the tray[s]</p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for 3-4 min or until the cheeze has melted and the brioche is warmed through</p>",
